    <h1>Design &amp; Tech News</h1>
    <p>New tools, AI trends, startup funding, and industry developments — curated daily for builders across Africa and beyond.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="search-bar">
      <span class="search-icon">🔍</span>
      <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Search news..." />
    </div>

    <div class="filter-bar">
      <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="ai">AI &amp; Design</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="africa">Africa Tech</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="tools">Tools</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="startups">Startups</button>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">

      <article class="news-card" data-category="ai">
        <div class="news-img news-img-1">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🤖</span>
          <span class="news-category">AI Design</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Figma AI Launches Auto-Layout Assistant for Complex Design Systems</h3>
          <p>Figma's new AI features automate tedious design-system tasks, generating component variants and auto-layout rules in seconds.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 18, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="africa">
        <div class="news-img news-img-2">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🌍</span>
          <span class="news-category">Africa Tech</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>African Startup Ecosystem Raises $2.4B in Q1 2025 — A 40% YoY Surge</h3>
          <p>Fintech continues to lead, but edtech and health-tech are gaining ground fast across East and West Africa.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 12, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="tools">
        <div class="news-img news-img-3">
          <span class="news-img-icon">⚡</span>
          <span class="news-category">Tools</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Vercel Introduces v0 AI: Generate Full-Stack Apps from Plain Text</h3>
          <p>Vercel's newest AI builder lets developers scaffold production-ready Next.js apps in minutes — no boilerplate required.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 8, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="startups">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0D2137 0%,#1E3A5F 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">💰</span>
          <span class="news-category">Funding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Wave Raises $137M Series B to Expand Mobile Money Across Francophone Africa</h3>
          <p>The Senegal-based fintech is expanding to five new markets after its latest round led by Stripe and Sequoia.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 5, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="ai">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1E0A3C 0%,#3B0764 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🎨</span>
          <span class="news-category">AI Design</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Adobe Firefly 3 Can Now Edit Photoshop Files Using Natural Language</h3>
          <p>Adobe's latest Firefly model understands complex design context and can make targeted edits across layered PSD files.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 2, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="africa">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#064E3B 0%,#0D2137 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🏆</span>
          <span class="news-category">Africa Tech</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Nigeria's Moniepoint Becomes Africa's Newest Unicorn with $1B Valuation</h3>
          <p>The Lagos-based business banking startup has processed over $182B in transactions and now serves 10M+ businesses.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">May 28, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="tools">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0F2256 0%,#0F172A 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🛠️</span>
          <span class="news-category">Tools</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>GitHub Copilot Now Integrates Directly Into Figma for Design-to-Code Handoffs</h3>
          <p>Microsoft's new integration bridges the gap between design and engineering by generating production-ready React components from Figma frames.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">May 22, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="startups">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1C1218 0%,#350D36 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🚀</span>
          <span class="news-category">Startups</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Linear Hits $1B ARR and Announces Major Enterprise Expansion</h3>
          <p>The beloved project management tool for engineers crosses a key revenue milestone and launches enterprise features targeting Fortune 500 companies.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">May 18, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="news-card" data-category="ai">
        <div class="news-img" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#052E16 0%,#0F172A 100%)">
          <span class="news-img-icon">🧠</span>
          <span class="news-category">AI</span>
        </div>
        <div class="news-body">
          <h3>Anthropic's Claude 4 Outperforms GPT-4o on Design and Code Generation Benchmarks</h3>
          <p>New evaluation results show Claude's latest model leads on complex UI generation tasks and multi-step code reasoning.</p>
          <div class="news-meta">
            <span class="date">May 14, 2025</span>
            <a href="post-template.html" class="read-more">Read more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

